- 12:00p - lunch (Brett's grill).
- 12:45p - cake (chocolate, buttercream, blue #10 candles). Norma - I
  remembered to make Chad a plate with less frosting, don't worry.
- 1:15p - presents.
- 2:30p - kids gone.
- 3:30p - UK vs Georgia Tech tips off on ESPN2. Yes I checked the
