- The birdhouse Chad is building - save it for Christmas Eve like we
  discussed. Christmas is Christmas, birthday is birthday.

HEALTH STUFF (Norma this is for you)
- Fridge stocked with the diet-friendly stuff. Diet Dr Pepper, plain
  yogurt, blueberries, whole grain bread.
- I moved the coffee decaf to the front of the cabinet so Chad doesn't
